snippet.title: The Other Shore | Strategy RPG Mobile Game CBT Trailer
snippet.description:
Strategy RPG mobile game The Other Shore released a new trailer and will launch its closed beta test on April 11.

On that day, the judgment came down. A world called "Abyss" is open to you.

#TheOtherShore #MobileGame #Gaming
